						<summary>

						<p>On a hero-stone set up by the side of the Guṇḍīśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Sarvadhāri, Māgha śu. 5 • • • • .</p>						

						<p>Records the death of Ādepa, son of Tupāki Siddhana, probably in a fight, on behalf of Veṅgaḷappa-Nāyuḍu. In characters of the 17th century A.D.</p>						

